      "Key": "6D6B76AF43CDC4D67959E596155991C3",
      "SourceString": "Thanos and his Chitauri horde invades the Battle Royale island, in search of the six Infinity Stones. Fighting against them is a team of heroes wielding mythic Avengers items.\r\n\r\nEach time a stone is found, Thanos & his army will grow more powerful. If all six are found, the heroes will no longer be able to respawn, and Thanos can eliminate those who remain to win. \r\n\r\nChitauri will respawn when eliminated until their army is decimated. They must help Thanos find the stones before this happens to achieve victory. ",
      "LocalizedString": "Thanos and his Chitauri horde invades the Battle Royale island, in search of the six Infinity Stones. Fighting against them is a team of heroes wielding mythic Avengers items.\r\n\r\nEach time a stone is found, Thanos & his army will grow more powerful. If all six are found, the heroes will no longer be able to respawn, and Thanos can eliminate those who remain to win. \r\n\r\nChitauri will respawn when eliminated until their army is decimated. They must help Thanos find the stones before this happens to achieve victory. "
